    dcterms:identifier "AI-0700" ;
    rdfs:comment "AI-powered creation of three-dimensional geometric models, volumetric representations, and 4D dynamic scenes using neural networks and machine learning techniques, including generative models, neural radiance fields, gaussian splatting, and diffusion-based 3D synthesis."@en ;
